{{Vgsname-nb|异度之刃|ja=ゼノブレイド，Xenoblade|en=Xenoblade Chronicles|diff=yes|cn=异度之刃|tw=异域神剑}}是由[[Monolith_Soft|Monolith Soft]]开发制作， [[任天堂|任天堂]]公司发行的[[电子角色扮演游戏|电子角色扮演游戏]]系列，制作人[[高橋哲哉_(遊戲製作人)|高桥哲哉]]。系列共有两款作品：2010年登陆[[Wii|Wii]]平台的《[[异度之刃|异度之刃]]》<ref>[https://web.archive.org/web/20100411210438/http://www.andriasang.com/e/blog/2010/04/08/xenoblade_site_update Date Set for Xenoblade]</ref>，和预定于2015年初登陆[[Wii_U|Wii U]]平台的[[精神续作|精神续作]]《[[异度之刃X|异度之刃X]]》<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2014/06/10/e3-2014-xenoblade-chronicles-x-coming-in-2015-2 |title=E3 2014: Xenoblade Chronicles X Coming in 2015 |access-date=2014-12-09 |archive-date=2014-06-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140619021150/http://www.ign.com/articles/2014/06/10/e3-2014-xenoblade-chronicles-x-coming-in-2015-2 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.siliconera.com/2014/06/13/xenoblade-chronicles-x-sequel-xenoblade/ |title=Xenoblade Chronicles X Is Not A Sequel To Xenoblade |access-date=2014-12-09 |archive-date=2015-10-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151013204542/http://www.siliconera.com/2014/06/13/xenoblade-chronicles-x-sequel-xenoblade/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。《异度之刃》预定于2015年发行掌上游戏机[[新任天堂3DS|新任天堂3DS]][[遊戲移植|移植]]版<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.siliconera.com/2014/08/29/xenoblade-chronicles-remake-announced-new-nintendo-3ds/ |title=Xenoblade Chronicles Announced For New Nintendo 3DS |access-date=2014-12-09 |archive-date=2015-09-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150909135718/http://www.siliconera.com/2014/08/29/xenoblade-chronicles-remake-announced-new-nintendo-3ds/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

